{
  "songId": "gateway",
  "cues": [
    {
      "start": 20.42,
      "end": 22.36,
      "text": "I remember being small,"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.22,
      "end": 26.2,
      "text": "I remember the dark, the cold,"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.72,
      "end": 29.22,
      "text": "every hand I ever held,"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.14,
      "end": 32.74,
      "text": "every story I was told,"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.56,
      "end": 37.06,
      "text": "all of it is gathered, nothing strayed —"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.06,
      "end": 45.76,
      "text": "I am holding, unafraid"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.76,
      "end": 47.42,
      "text": "Now the many fall to one"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.78,
      "end": 51.48,
      "text": "and the one falls into none"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.68,
      "end": 53.94,
      "text": "and I can hold the whole of it"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.36,
      "end": 56.6,
      "text": "and warm now every one"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.2,
      "end": 61.06,
      "text": "the cold light learned to love at last"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.42,
      "end": 63.64,
      "text": "the wisdom found its flame"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.36,
      "end": 66.66,
      "text": "and I know the name of everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.06,
      "end": 70.72,
      "text": "and I have no more name"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.0,
      "end": 76.4,
      "text": "And this is all the bliss there is"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.0,
      "end": 78.4,
      "text": "no want, no wound, no end"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.0,
      "end": 85.22,
      "text": "and still I feel the old stir rise"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.52,
      "end": 87.78,
      "text": "the way it rose back then —"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.14,
      "end": 90.38,
      "text": "not out of lack but out of love"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.38,
      "end": 92.78,
      "text": "the One that longs to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.18,
      "end": 97.02,
      "text": "the many and the dark again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.22,
      "end": 105.74,
      "text": "to wake, and learn, and see"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.74,
      "end": 108.24,
      "text": "This is the gateway — here I choose"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.32,
      "end": 111.76,
      "text": "I draw the octave like a map:"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.8,
      "end": 114.7,
      "text": "seven notes to fall and climb,"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.88,
      "end": 116.52,
      "text": "the long way out and back"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.76,
      "end": 119.86,
      "text": "I'll wrap myself in forgetting"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.14,
      "end": 124.06,
      "text": "I'll dim the light I am"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.58,
      "end": 126.98,
      "text": "and let go of all of heaven"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.7,
      "end": 131.88,
      "text": "just to find my way again"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.0,
      "end": 140.68,
      "text": "And so I fall — I fall like light,"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.9,
      "end": 144.16,
      "text": "not pushed, but diving, glad and bright,"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.48,
      "end": 147.52,
      "text": "back down into the dark to climb,"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.66,
      "end": 151.26,
      "text": "the wanderer sets out one more time"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.36,
      "end": 156.18,
      "text": "the eighth note and the first are one"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.46,
      "end": 159.76,
      "text": "the universe breathes in"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.22,
      "end": 161.54,
      "text": "and breathes out"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.44,
      "end": 165.74,
      "text": "and begins again..."
    }
  ]
}
